title: Part A
stimulusHtml:
1 point is earned for the implicit differentiation

1 point is earned if solved for y'

2yy'=y+xy'

(2y-x)y'=y

descriptions:
The student response earns none of the following points:

1 point is earned for the implicit differentiation

1 point is earned if solved for y'

2yy'=y+xy'

(2y-x)y'=y

y'= y 2y−x

The student response earns one of the following points:

1 point is earned for the implicit differentiation

1 point is earned if solved for y'

2yy'=y+xy'

(2y-x)y'=y

y'= y 2y−x

The student response earns all of the following points:

1 point is earned for the implicit differentiation

1 point is earned if solved for y'

2yy'=y+xy'

(2y-x)y'=y

y'= y 2y−x
